&lt;p&gt;We are looking for enthusiastic and motivated team players to join our friendly operating theatre department.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will be a registered Nurse or Operating Department Practitioner or due to qualify this year.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are offering positions in either scrub or anaesthetic roles.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We will support learning and development and encourage skill mixing in both areas.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We deliver a range of surgical specialties including emergency, trauma and obstetric cover&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Informal visits are encouraged&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
